Request body:

```json
{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "organizationId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "type": 1,
  "channel": 1,
  "variables": {
    "full_name": "Иван Иванов",
    "login": "ivan"
  },
  "customMessage": null,
  "preferredLanguage": 1
